Trevor Manuel urged South Africans to look beyond the African National Congress (ANC) and take responsibility for their national project, otherwise the country might be headed for a Trump-like future. The former minister of finance and member of the ANC's National Executive Committee (NEC) berated South Africans at the launch of the Huffington Post South Africa on Sunday for not being "out on the streets" protesting against a wayward president.

